                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <a href='https://apps.apple.com/us/app/travellingyuan/id1539742230?itsct=apps_box&itscg=30200' style='display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 13px; width: 250px; height: 83px;'><img src='https://tools.applemediaservices.com/api/badges/download-on-the-app-store/black/en-US?size=250x83&amp;releaseDate=1589155200&h=7baf411acf21a6aee0a1e5a7e083481c' alt='Download on the App Store' style='border-radius: 13px; width: 250px; height: 83px;'></a>
